fields.product_name: My Protein Impact Whey Protein Unflavoured 1KG

fields.product_description: Our Extreme Gainer Blend has been created specifically to support your bulk-up ambitions, with a huge 35g of protein per serving — perfect for building and maintaining muscle.

fields.product_name: My Protein Impact Whey Isolate Unflavoured 1KG
fields.product_description: Packed with 23g of protein per serving, this superior-quality blend is ideal to provide your muscles with the protein they need for growth and maintenance,1 so that you can keep making progress with your fitness goals.

fields.product_name: My Protein Weight Gainer Blend Unflavoured 2.5KG
fields.product_description: If you’re looking to gain weight, build strength, or increase size then you’re going to have to consume more calories than you burn throughout the day. To gain muscle you must combine a calorie surplus, with high-quality protein sources, which contributes to the growth and maintenance of muscle mass and a well thoughtout strength training plan.

fields.product_name: My Protein Creatine Monohydrate 250 Unflavoured Tablets
fields.product_description: Our creatine monohydrate tablets are a super-convenient way to get the scientifically proven benefits of creatine, helping you to improve your performance workout after workout.

fields.product_name: My Protein A-Z Multivitamin 90 Tablets
fields.product_description: Vitamins and minerals are essential nutrients needed to maintain a healthy body and mind. They help to keep us in top condition, despite hectic lives and training schedules. Our A-Z Multivitamin delivers a unique formula of essential vitamins and minerals, boasting great health benefits for everyday wellbeing.

fields.product_name: My Protein Pure Caffeine 100 Unflavoured Tablets

fields.product_name: My Protein Daily Multivitamin 180 Tablets
fields.product_description: Vitamins are essential to maintaining overall health and wellbeing, performing many important functions in the body making it vital you hit your recommended daily requirements.

fields.product_name: My Protein Chocolate Sundae Layered Protein Bars, Box Of 12
fields.product_description: Our Layered Protein Bar is our most indulgent protein bar yet, created to be a guilt-free and delicious snack to support your fitness ambitions.

fields.product_name: My Protein Chocolate Protein Brownies, Box Of 12
fields.product_description: With up to 75% less sugar than standard supermarket alternatives, enjoy an afternoon pick-me-up without ruining all your hard earned progress. fields.product_name: My Protein Double Chocolate Cereal Bars, Box Of 18
fields.product_description: Snacking can be tough, especially if you are trying to keep your calorie intake low. Created from a delicious blend of soya protein and oats, our Cereal Bar is packed with more than 4.5g of protein and are 100kcal and under, it’s perfect for making sure you’re getting the protein you need, each and every day while counting your calories.

fields.product_name: My Protein Chocolate Protein Break Bars, Box Of 16
fields.product_description: Made with real milk chocolate and layers of crispy wafer, these are a sweet solution to your cravings plus, with more than double the amount of protein as supermarket alternatives, they’re a perfect support for your training routine.
